div.p: Greetings! I am Barrett Harber, from Tampa, FL, USA. I started off my career in military intelligence, but transitioned into software development later on, as I've had a passion for development since I was a kid. Right now, I'm doing DevOps consulting work for @stelligent.

I'm currently working on @quipt, which is a videoboard web app that uses a number of different technologies and runs on @aws. In support of @quipt, I also work on @ffbuilds, which is an ffmpeg build project. I've also contributed to several open source projects over the years and have created a few myself.

If you choose to sponsor me, I will use the funds to help pay for my AWS bill, which is admittedly not much as everything is serverless, but there are still some costs associated with running @quipt such as Route53, CodeBuild, S3 storage, etc.

p.strong: Thank you for time and consideration!
